function Start(idActor, snoQuest)
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Hawe_Coast_LyndonGoon_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
		-- Wait a beat after the vignette
		Hydra.QActorWait(idFollower, 2.0)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_Orton_ChestCallout, idFollower, idSelf)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, id_Orton, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idFollower, id_Orton)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idFollower)
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(id_Orton)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, marker_Orton_RunTo, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idClone)
	end
end
